Awesome iPhone', 'review_text': "I previously had the original iPhone SE from 2016, I bought it brand new in I believe 2019. That phone was perfect for me. i would still be using it had the screen not decided to die out of the blue. The specs are the same as the iPhone 13 so newest CPU and GPU, internals are all the same except the size of the battery (I get 2 full days on a charge right now).. Everything runs smooth and nice and no problems.If you want the better internals of an iPhone but dont want to spend a huge ton of more money, this would be for you.
